 I'm not sure what happens to the Feynmann path integrals at the EH, though.
 I guess this is the big stink about the firewall problem, eh?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
One step at a time.
 We seem to have demonstrated a 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

firewall
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 at the classical level.
 We now need to develop the geometric machinery to explicitly exhibit it.
